links: Vincenzo Librandi, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
maple: P:=proc(i) local a,b,c,n; for n from 1 by 1 to i do a:=evalf(floor(log10(n^3)+1)); b:=n^3; c:=0; while a>0 do c:=c+(b-(trunc(b/10)*10))*10^(a-1); b:=trunc(b/10); a:=a-1; od; print(c); od; end: P(100); # _Paolo P. Lava_, Aug 07 2008
